{"id": "svg1665702629592", "title": "Frame", "breadcrumbs": ["Uniface Reference", "Development Object and Property Reference", "Development Object Properties", "Presentation Properties", "FRM Widget Properties for Fields", "Frame"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/svg1665702629592.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">Frame</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous:   Frame \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous:   Frame \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/unq1665703080772.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next: Frame Width (FrameWidth) \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next: Frame Width (FrameWidth) \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qyp1665702633319.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/svg1665702629592.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/svg1665702629592.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/svg1665702629592.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3615979\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3615979\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 07, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104svg1665702629592.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/svg1665702629592.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/svg1665702629592.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"svg1665702629592\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines whether a border is displayed around the widget at run time. <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>. The default value depends on the widget.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"svg1665702629592__topic_d104009e1_d104010e1_d104011e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"svg1665702629592__p_d104012e1_d104013e1_d104014e1\">Frame<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code></p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"svg1665702629592__table_d12275e1_d12276e1_d12277e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"svg1665702629592__table_d12275e1_d12276e1_d12277e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"svg1665702629592__table_d12275e1_d12276e1_d12277e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"svg1665702629592__table_d12275e1_d12276e1_d12277e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"svg1665702629592__table_d12275e1_d12276e1_d12277e1__entry__2\">Border is displayed.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"svg1665702629592__table_d12275e1_d12276e1_d12277e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"svg1665702629592__table_d12275e1_d12276e1_d12277e1__entry__2\">Border is not displayed.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"svg1665702629592__section_w845ab1b5b3_w846ab1b5_w847ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d139862e117\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"svg1665702629592__table_d12278e1_d12279e1_d12280e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Depends on widget</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dynamic?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Depends on widget</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Supported in Grid?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dependencies:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">When <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>, other properties\n                        can be used to style the border.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"svg1665702629592__section_m2g_gyn_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d139862e175\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"svg1665702629592__p_d104021e1_d104022e1_d104023e1\">When <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Frame</span> is selected, the\n            appearance of the frame is determined by the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">3-D Effect</span> property.\n            If <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">3-D Effect</span> is <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>, the border is 1-pixel\n            wide and the color is determined by Windows. If <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">3-D Effect</span> is\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>, a three-dimensional border is displayed.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"svg1665702629592__section_ffn_jyn_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d139862e203\">Edit Box and Rich Edit Box</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"svg1665702629592__p_d104027e1_d104028e1_d104029e1\">In the Edit Box and Rich Edit Box widgets, the\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Frame</span> property can be changed dynamically in Proc, but only if\n            the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">3-D Effect</span> property is <code class=\"ph codeph\">false</code> when the form\n            is initialized (for example, in the widget properties dialog or before an\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">edit</span> statement in the exec operation). It is not possible to\n            change the  3D property dynamically, so you cannot\n            apply a 3D appearance to a border that is dynamically applied.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"svg1665702629592__pre_mpn_kyn_wwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">; toggle Frame property\nif ($properties(FLD1) = \"frame=false\")\n $properties(FLD1) = \"frame=true\"\nelse\n $properties(FLD1) = \"frame=false\"\nendif</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"svg1665702629592__section_pbt_lyn_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d139862e229\">Drop Down List</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"svg1665702629592__p_d104033e1_d104034e1_d104035e1\">For the drop-down list widget, the border is\n            displayed only if both <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Frame</span> and <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Dynamic</span>\n            are <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>, and the field does not have focus. In this case, it is\n            possible to set the color of the border using the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Frame Color</span>\n            property.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"svg1665702629592__section_l5z_myn_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d139862e251\">TabEx</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"svg1665702629592__p_d104039e1_d104040e1_d104041e1\">For the Tabex widget, it is possible to specify the\n            width and color of the border using the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Frame Width</span> and\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Frame Color</span> properties.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"svg1665702629592__section_hw2_4yn_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d139862e266\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"svg1665702629592__ul_ts4_pyn_wwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"svg1665702629592__li_d41672e1_d41673e1_d41674e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kzn1665703126224.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kzn1665703126224.html\" title=\"The ucolorbox widget displays a color value, either a color name or RGB value, in a color box in a form component. Uniface provides a logical widget called ColorBox, which is mapped to ucolorbox.\">ucolorbox (ColorBox)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"svg1665702629592__li_d41675e1_d41676e1_d41677e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gzs1665702629046.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gzs1665702629046.html\" title=\"The (ucolorlist) widget displays a list of system or web colors for selection in a form component. Uniface provides a logical widget called ColorList, which is mapped to ucolorlist.\">ucolorlist (ColorList)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"svg1665702629592__li_d41678e1_d41679e1_d41680e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vmo1688449724415.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vmo1688449724415.html\" title=\"The ucombobox widget combines an input field with a drop-down list. It allows users to select one item from a previously defined list, or enter their own data instead. It is applicable only to form components. Uniface provides a logical widget called ComboBox, which is mapped to ucombobox.\">ucombobox (Combo Box)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"svg1665702629592__li_d41681e1_d41682e1_d41683e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wrn1665702633674.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wrn1665702633674.html\" title=\"The DropTarget logical widget accepts input dragged from a DragSource, other Uniface application, or Microsoft Windows Explorer. The data that is transferred consists of a Uniface list.\">DropTarget</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"svg1665702629592__li_d41684e1_d41685e1_d41686e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fud1688450548955.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fud1688450548955.html\" title=\"The udropdownlist widget is a field-level widget that can display a list of valid options in a list below the input field, so that the user can select one. It is applicable only to form components.\">udropdownlist (DropDownList)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"svg1665702629592__li_d41687e1_d41688e1_d41689e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"klb1688454363706.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/klb1688454363706.html\" title=\"Default logical widget for entering and displaying data in a field in a Form or Report.\">EditBox</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"svg1665702629592__li_d41690e1_d41691e1_d41692e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gev1665702640020.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gev1665702640020.html\" title=\"The ucontainer widget embeds a non-modal form in a field of the current form. Uniface provides a logical widget called FormContainer, which is mapped to ucontainer.\">ucontainer (FormContainer)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"svg1665702629592__li_d41693e1_d41694e1_d41695e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ied1665702642247.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ied1665702642247.html\" title=\"The uhtml widget is a field-level widget in a form component that renders HTML code (including HTML, CSS, and JavaScript) or displays a web page (when the field value is a URL prefixed by an ampersand (&amp;www.mysite.com/doc/index.html). Uniface provides a logical widget called HTML, which is mapped to uhtml.\">uhtml (HTML Widget)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"svg1665702629592__li_d41696e1_d41697e1_d41698e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rez1688451198680.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rez1688451198680.html\" title=\"The ulistbox widget is a field-level widget that displays an open list in which one or more values can be selected. It can only be used in form components.\">ulistbox (ListBox )</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"svg1665702629592__li_d41699e1_d41700e1_d41701e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gls1665702643795.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gls1665702643795.html\" title=\"The umap widget defines areas on an image that allow the user to interact by clicking on that area. It can only be used in form components. Uniface provides a logical widget called Map, which is mapped to umap.\">umap (Map)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"svg1665702629592__li_d41702e1_d41703e1_d41704e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bwv1665702644903.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bwv1665702644903.html\" title=\"The umeter widget displays the value of a Numeric field on a gauge for which there is a predefined range of values marked around the outer edge. Uniface provides a logical widget called Meter, which is mapped to umeter.\">umeter (Meter)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"svg1665702629592__li_d41705e1_d41706e1_d41707e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"svk1665702646925.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/svk1665702646925.html\" title=\"The umonthcalendar widget displays a month calendar to enable the user to select a date. Uniface provides a logical widget called MonthCalendar, which is mapped to umonthcalendar.\">(umonthcalendar) MonthCalendar</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"svg1665702629592__li_d41708e1_d41709e1_d41710e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vvo1665702647716.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vvo1665702647716.html\" title=\"The uOcxContainer widget embeds a Microsoft OCX control into a form component, and maps OCX properties and OCX events to fields and triggers. You can use ProcScript to activate OCX methods and let the OCX control activate widget triggers to respond to OCX events.\">uOcxContainer (OcxContainer)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"svg1665702629592__li_d41711e1_d41712e1_d41713e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rdo1665702649920.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rdo1665702649920.html\" title=\"The uOleContainer widget displays an embedded OLE object, enabling you to define links to OLE objects in Uniface applications.\">uOleContainer (OleContainer)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"svg1665702629592__li_d41714e1_d41715e1_d41716e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ddd1665702643397.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ddd1665702643397.html\" title=\"The uoutputbox widget displays streaming text data. The data may come from a specified Output Channel, or be explicitly added. By default, it does not listen to any channel. Uniface provides a logical widget called OutputBox, which is mapped to uoutputbox.\">uoutputbox (OutputBox)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"svg1665702629592__li_d41717e1_d41718e1_d41719e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yye1665702650577.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yye1665702650577.html\" title=\"The uradiogroup widget displays a set of mutually exclusive choices as a group of radio buttons. Uniface provides a logical widget called RadioGroup, which is mapped to uradiogroup.\">uradiogroup (RadioGroup)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"svg1665702629592__li_d41720e1_d41721e1_d41722e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qwk1688451210612.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qwk1688451210612.html\" title=\"The urtfeditbox widget is used to display and edit text as Rich Text Format (RTF), which supports formatting such as font and color attributes, text alignment, indentation, and lists. Uniface provides a logical widget called RichEditBox, which is mapped to urtfeditbox.\">urtfeditbox (RichEditBox)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"svg1665702629592__li_d41723e1_d41724e1_d41725e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"foe1665702651174.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/foe1665702651174.html\" title=\"The uslider widget allows users to edit a numeric value in a field by sliding an indicator in a set of a previously defined range of values. Uniface provides a logical widget called Slider, which is mapped to uslider.\">uslider (Slider)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"svg1665702629592__li_d41726e1_d41727e1_d41728e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lxs1665702651483.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lxs1665702651483.html\" title=\"The uspinbutton widget enables the user to enter or select a numeric value by clicking a button to increase or decrease a value by a predefined interval within a predefined range. Uniface provides a logical widget called SpinButton, which is mapped to uspinbutton.\">uspinbutton (SpinButton)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"svg1665702629592__li_d41729e1_d41730e1_d41731e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gyf1688451219719.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gyf1688451219719.html\" title=\"The utabex widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. The utabex widget is highly customizable, allowing extensive control over the appearance and behavior of the tabs. Uniface provides a logical widget called TabEx, which is mapped to utabex.\">utabex (TabEx)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"svg1665702629592__li_d41732e1_d41733e1_d41734e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gge1665702634237.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gge1665702634237.html\" title=\"The utree widget enables users to view and navigate structured data as a hierarchy. Uniface provides a logical widget called Tree, which is mapped to utree.\">utree (Tree)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qyp1665702633319.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Frame Width (FrameWidth)</a><p>Width of the border around the widget in pixels, if Frame is true. Default is 1 pixel.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/txj1665702628158.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>3-D Effect (3d)</a><p>This property determines whether a three-dimensional appearance is applied when the widget is displayed. True (default) or False.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sdz1665702638839.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Dynamic</a><p>Determines how the widget is displayed if the field does not have focus.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gby1665702633390.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Frame Color (FrameColor)</a><p>The Frame Color widget property determines the color of the frame around the widget, if a frame is specified.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615979\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615979\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Frame Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 07, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Determines whether a border is displayed around the widget at run time. True or False . The default value depends on the widget. Frame = True | False Value Description True Border is displayed. False Border is not displayed. Usage Default value Depends on widget Dynamic? Depends on widget Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: When True , other properties can be used to style the border. Description When Frame is selected, the appearance of the frame is determined by the 3-D Effect property. If 3-D Effect is False , the border is 1-pixel wide and the color is determined by Windows. If 3-D Effect is True , a three-dimensional border is displayed. Edit Box and Rich Edit Box In the Edit Box and Rich Edit Box widgets, the Frame property can be changed dynamically in Proc, but only if the 3-D Effect property is false when the form is initialized (for example, in the widget properties dialog or before an edit statement in the exec operation). It is not possible to change the 3D property dynamically, so you cannot apply a 3D appearance to a border that is dynamically applied. ; toggle Frame property if ($properties(FLD1) = \"frame=false\") $properties(FLD1) = \"frame=true\" else $properties(FLD1) = \"frame=false\" endif Copy Drop Down List For the drop-down list widget, the border is displayed only if both Frame and Dynamic are True , and the field does not have focus. In this case, it is possible to set the color of the border using the Frame Color property. TabEx For the Tabex widget, it is possible to specify the width and color of the border using the Frame Width and Frame Color properties. Applies To ucolorbox (ColorBox) ucolorlist (ColorList) ucombobox (Combo Box) DropTarget udropdownlist (DropDownList) EditBox ucontainer (FormContainer) uhtml (HTML Widget) ulistbox (ListBox ) umap (Map) umeter (Meter) (umonthcalendar) MonthCalendar uOcxContainer (OcxContainer) uOleContainer (OleContainer) uoutputbox (OutputBox) uradiogroup (RadioGroup) urtfeditbox (RichEditBox) uslider (Slider) uspinbutton (SpinButton) utabex (TabEx) utree (Tree) Related Links Frame Width (FrameWidth) Width of the border around the widget in pixels, if Frame is true. Default is 1 pixel. 3-D Effect (3d) This property determines whether a three-dimensional appearance is applied when the widget is displayed. True (default) or False. Dynamic Determines how the widget is displayed if the field does not have focus. Frame Color (FrameColor) The Frame Color widget property determines the color of the frame around the widget, if a frame is specified. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}